                              Размеры полей: левое 2,0.</seg>
                          <seg xml:lang="en"><rs type="execution" ref="execution.xml#scalpro"/> On the front. Broken off on all sides, except the left; chipped and pitted in some spots and blackened as a result of fire. 
                          Margins: left 2,0.</seg>
